prompts.frontCover: A charming watercolor painting of a very determined, slightly wobbly snail wearing a tiny, festive party hat, heroically carrying a giant, brightly decorated birthday cake on its shell. The cake is comically oversized, tilting precariously, with melting candles. Below the snail, a trail of shimmering, colorful slime sparkles on the ground. Centered on the card, in beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script, is the text "happy birthday... I got here as fast as I could!". The style is flat 2D for printing, with soft flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, visible paper texture, and organic paint bleeds, creating a humorous and lighthearted scene. --style raw
